                "invention-title": [
                    "Comprehensive utilization system of clean energy",
                    "清洁能源的综合利用系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a comprehensive utilization system for clean energy, and belongs to the technical field of energy utilization. A comprehensive utilization system of clean energy comprises a power consumption device used for storing power of a micro-grid; the hydrogen generation device is connected with the electric power consumption device and is used for electrolyzing the electric power generated by the electric power consumption device into hydrogen; the hydrogen consumption device is connected with the hydrogen generation device and is used for receiving the hydrogen and storing the hydrogen or using the hydrogen; the dispatching device is in signal connection with the power consumption device, the hydrogen generation device and the hydrogen consumption device; wherein the scheduling device is used for adjusting the hydrogen generation rate of the hydrogen generation device according to the power consumption capability of the power consumption device and the hydrogen consumption capability of the hydrogen consumption device. According to the technical scheme, the construction cost of a miniaturized solar power station and a miniaturized wind power station can be reduced, and the utilization rate of solar energy and wind energy is increased."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请公开了清洁能源的综合利用系统，属于能源利用技术领域。一种清洁能源的综合利用系统，包括，电力消纳装置，用于储存微网的电力；氢气生成装置，与电力消纳装置连接，用于将电力消纳装置所产生的电力电解为氢气；氢气消纳装置，与氢气生成装置连接，用于接收氢气，并将氢气储存或者使用氢气；调度装置，分别与电力消纳装置、氢气生成装置，以及氢气消纳装置信号连接；其中，调度装置用于根据电力消纳装置的电力消纳能力和氢气消纳装置的氢气消纳能力调整氢气生成装置的氢气生成速率。本申请所提供的技术方案能够减少小型化的太阳能发电站和风能发电站的建造成本，增加太阳能和风能的利用率。"
                }
            ]
